snippet.title: Dig Dug Revival (Dig Dug remake for Windows) (by Luca Carminati, LC-Games)
snippet.description:
Download Dig Dug Revival from https://lowcarb.itch.io

This game is a homage to Dig Dug, an arcade game developed by Namco in 1982.

In this version, except the first one, the playfields are generated randomly.

Author: Luca Carminati (lucacarminati1967@gmail.com)

Read the "ReadMe.txt" file for more info.
